---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Website Development That Generates Leads | OpsHQ Digital"
  description="Fast, SEO-optimized websites that generate leads — not just look pretty. Modern stack, minimal hosting costs. Seattle developer."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-950 to-navy-800 text-white py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 max-w-3xl">Is Your Website Costing You Customers?</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-2xl">If your site is slow, invisible on Google, or not bringing in leads — it's a liability, not an asset.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-6">Your Website Should Be Your Best Salesperson</h2>
      <div class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>Your website should be working 24/7, answering questions, and generating leads. Instead, it's probably a WordPress site from 2019 with a $100+/month hosting bill, slow load times, and zero leads last quarter.</p>
        <p>Modern web development isn't about picking a template. It's about building a fast, search-optimized machine that actually brings customers to your door.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-12 text-center">Websites That Work as Hard as You Do</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">⚡</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">Blazing-Fast Sites</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Built on modern frameworks that score 95+ on Google PageSpeed. Fast sites rank higher and convert better. Period.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🔍</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">SEO-First Architecture</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Proper keyword targeting, schema markup, sitemaps, and Core Web Vitals optimization. Built to rank on Google from day one.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📩</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">Lead Capture</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Contact forms, consultation booking, click-to-call — everything instrumented for conversion tracking so you know what's working.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">💰</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">Right-Sized Hosting</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Optimized cloud infrastructure that eliminates bloated hosting bills. Modern sites don't need expensive servers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📰</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">Content Platforms</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Blog systems with category management, author profiles, and automated social distribution.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📊</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">Analytics Built In</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Google Analytics, Search Console, and heatmap tracking so you can see exactly where visitors come from.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Results -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-6">Real Results</h2>
      <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">We built a content platform that went from:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
          <li>• <strong>$100+/month WordPress</strong> hosting to a <strong>fraction of that cost</strong></li>
          <li>• <strong>Zero Google presence</strong> to <strong>page-one rankings</strong> in under 6 weeks</li>
          <li>• <strong>35+ published posts</strong> with automated social distribution</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/work/content-platform/" class="inline-block mt-4 text-blue-500 font-medium hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Read the full case study →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 group" open>
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-950 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            How much does a website cost?
            <span class="text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Most websites run $2,500 – $10,000 depending on size and complexity. We provide a fixed-price quote after the discovery call.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 group">
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-950 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            How long does it take?
            <span class="text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Most websites launch within 2-4 weeks. Complex sites with custom functionality may take 4-6 weeks.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 group">
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-950 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Will my site show up on Google?
            <span class="text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Yes. Every site we build includes SEO-first architecture — proper keywords, schema markup, sitemap submission, and Core Web Vitals optimization.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 group">
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-950 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Do I need to know how to code to update my site?
            <span class="text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">No. We'll set up a system that lets you update content easily, or we can handle updates for you as part of a maintenance plan.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Straightforward Pricing</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-2">Most web projects: <span class="font-bold text-navy-950">$2,500 – $10,000</span></p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-8">Monthly maintenance available starting at $500/month.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-950 to-navy-800 text-white py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Let's Build a Website That Earns Its Keep</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-8">Every project starts with a free discovery call. No commitment, no sales pitch.</p>
      <a href="/contact/?service=web" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-500 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors min-h-[44px] text-lg">
        Request a Discovery Call
      </a>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-400">
        <a href="/services/crm/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">CRM Development →</a>
        <a href="/services/ai/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">AI Automation →</a>
        <a href="/services/cloud/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Cloud & DevOps →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@graph": [
        {
          "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
          "itemListElement": [
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://opshqdigital.com/" },
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Services", "item": "https://opshqdigital.com/services/" },
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Web Development", "item": "https://opshqdigital.com/services/web/" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "@type": "ProfessionalService",
          "name": "Web Development — OpsHQ Digital",
          "url": "https://opshqdigital.com/services/web/",
          "description": "Fast, SEO-optimized websites that generate leads — not just look pretty. Modern stack, minimal hosting costs.",
          "provider": { "@id": "https://opshqdigital.com/#organization" },
          "areaServed": { "@type": "City", "name": "Seattle", "addressRegion": "WA" },
          "priceRange": "$2,500 – $10,000"
        },
        {
          "@type": "FAQPage",
          "mainEntity": [
            { "@type": "Question", "name": "How much does a website cost?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Most websites run $2,500 – $10,000 depending on size and complexity. We provide a fixed-price quote after the discovery call." }},
            { "@type": "Question", "name": "How long does it take?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Most websites launch within 2-4 weeks. Complex sites with custom functionality may take 4-6 weeks." }},
            { "@type": "Question", "name": "Will my site show up on Google?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. Every site we build includes SEO-first architecture — proper keywords, schema markup, sitemap submission, and Core Web Vitals optimization." }},
            { "@type": "Question", "name": "Do I need to know how to code to update my site?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "No. We'll set up a system that lets you update content easily, or we can handle updates for you as part of a maintenance plan." }}
          ]
        }
      ]
    })} />
  </Fragment>
</BaseLayout>
